### Banner API Test (Public)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4001/api/v1

### 1. Get all active banners (Default)
GET {{baseUrl}}/banners
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Get active banners by placement (home_hero)
GET {{baseUrl}}/banners?placement=home_hero
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Get active banners by placement (promotion_bar)
GET {{baseUrl}}/banners?placement=promotion_bar
Content-Type: application/json
